
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Life isn&#8217;t a game, my friend<br />
Coming to the world has its price<br />
Friendship is eternal, my friend<br />
Love is in the core of man</p>
<p>Life is like a carousel<br />
It also has its ups and downs<br />
Lucky are those who go up my friend<br />
But by those who go down stand true friends</p>
<p>To breathe is not to live<br />
Living is thinking and feeling<br />
Regret the days gone without joy<br />
The carousel goes up and down my friend</p>
